{"word":"Gilead","slug":"gilead","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Gilead</b> <a href=\"#/H1568\">H1568</a> <br/> 1. A region east of the Jordan:<br/> - Allotted to the tribes of Reuben and Gad and half tribe of Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=30'>Num 32:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=13'>Deu 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=1'>Deu 34:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=33'>2Ki 10:33</a> <br/> - Reubenites expel the Hagarites from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=10'>1Ch 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=22'>1Ch 5:22</a> <br/> - Ammonites make war against; defeated by Jephthah<br/> <a href='B:'></a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=13'>Amo 1:13</a> <br/> - The prophet Elijah, a native of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=1'>1Ki 17:1</a> <br/> - David retreats to, at the time of Absalom's rebellion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=16'>2Sa 17:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=22'>2Sa 17:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=24'>2Sa 17:24</a> <br/> - David pursued into, by Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=26'>2Sa 17:26</a> <br/> - Absalom defeated and slain in the forests of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=9'>2Sa 18:9</a> <br/> - Hazael, king of Syria, smites the land of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=33'>2Ki 10:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=3'>Amo 1:3</a> <br/> - Invaded by Tiglath-Pileser, king of Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=29'>2Ki 15:29</a> <br/> - A grazing country<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=1'>Num 32:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=9'>1Ch 5:9</a> <br/> - Exported spices, balm, and myrrh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=25'>Gen 37:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=8&verse=22'>Jer 8:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=11'>Jer 46:11</a> <br/> - Figurative of prosperity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=6'>Jer 22:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=19'>Jer 50:19</a> <br/> 2. A mountain:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=3'>Jdg 7:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=4&verse=1'>Son 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=6&verse=5'>Son 6:5</a> <br/> - Laban overtakes Jacob at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=25'>Gen 31:25</a> <br/> 3. A city<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=6&verse=8'>Hos 6:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=12&verse=11'>Hos 12:11</a><br/> 4. Grandson of Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=30'>Num 26:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=1'>Num 27:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=36&verse=1'>Num 36:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=1'>Jos 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=3'>Jos 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=21'>1Ch 2:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=23'>1Ch 2:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=14'>1Ch 7:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=17'>1Ch 7:17</a><br/> 5. Father of Jephthah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=2'>Jdg 11:2</a><br/> 6. A chief of Gad<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=14'>1Ch 5:14</a>"}]}